"     Christopher P Cannon, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?25/7/25721/contributors\">",
"     Juan Carlos Kaski, MD, DM, DSc, FRCP, FESC, FACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
